---

## Project Features
- **Smart Scheduling** – Syncs with class schedules or allows manual input for automated ride matching.  
- **In-App Chat & Ratings** – Secure communication between students and a rating system for safety.  
- **Eco-Friendly Tracking** – Calculates CO₂ reduction and rewards active carpoolers.  

---

